name: Based Turbo
description: A memecoin for the people Turbo Token began as a bold experiment in cryptocurrency creation on mainnet Ethereum. Inspired by the power of artificial intelligence, the project's creator turned to GPT-4 with a simple challenge: create the next great meme coin, starting with a budget of just $69. To pay homage to our mainnet counterpart and for those of us that missed their entries, we bring you Based Turbo!
